      <bpmn2:documentation id="_2F1E9145-9212-4A03-90B2-E2121083E066"><![CDATA[Find a CAGE under the deployed cpeCrossId via CROSS PROJECT API. (FIND - depends on created cpeCrossId)]]></bpmn2:documentation>
